fetchAsDocument

Document fetchAsDocument(String url)
                         throws SAXException,
                                IOException
Retrieves a specified URL and return the response of request as Document. Assumes that is a GET request. Remember that Document class just parse XML content. So, if you need another type of response, try use fetchAsInputStream(String).

Parameters:
url - The url to fetch.
method - The method type of fetch.
Returns:
The content result of fetch.
